```{r}
data5b <- read.csv("~/dsan-5000-project-kendallgilbert180/dsan-website/5000-website/data/00-raw-data/5b.csv", header=FALSE, comment.char="#")
data5b <- data5b[-1,]
head(data5b)
data5b <- setNames(data5b, c("Country","2000","2001","2003","2004","2005","2006","2007","2008","2009", "2010", "2011","2012","2013","2014","2015","2016","2017", "2018", "2019", "2020", "2021","2022", "2023"))
data5b[data5b == ".."] <- NA
write.csv(data5b, file = "cleandata5b.csv", row.names = TRUE)
```
